== AZLOCO Ubuntu Hours Page ==

Welcome to the AZLOCO Ubuntu Hours page.  AZLOCO hosts four Ubuntu Hours each month, two in Tempe on the 1st and 4th Thursdays of each month, one in Phoenix on the 2nd Thursday of each month, and one in Sierra Vista on the 2nd Thursday of each month.

=== Ubuntu Hours ===
